thread.title: Christine Warr

author: Christine Warr
title: Christine Warr
text: Received their email on specials and spotted a 2 night Melb to Syd Cruise, reserved online an then rang and finalised the booking for 4. Easy as that, very efficient, pleasant and helped me with gathering the information required for the other passengers...I have cruised many times before but wanted to expose some friends and family to cruising and this was the prime opportunity. Thanks Cruisesalefinder....
